    <h3>What is Mechanical Engineering</h3>
    <div style='width: 700px; padding-top:25px; text-align: justify'>
      <p>Mechanical Engineering invloves studying mechanical/structural principles and components to the lowest level possible. 
      These skills are used together to build a variety of different products that are vitally important for people; 
      ranging from the cars to pipelines retrieving oil from beneath the ocean floor.</p>
    </div>
    <h3>Is this for you?</h3>
    <div style='width: 700px; padding-top:25px; text-align: justify'>
      <p>A love for mathematics, physical science and problem solving will serve as a good starting place. Interest in 
      how mechanical components work on their own or in a system could mean that this is just right for you. </p>
    </div>
